title: [No Noose Is Good Noose]
description: Each plank that makes up the small interior has been painted a different hideously garish shade, the colors vividly clashing with the stark white painted floor.  Garlands of feathers adorn the back wall, the chartreuse plumes suspending a haphazard looking shelf.  A small rack shaped to look like a grinning mouth rests on the floor just above a sign that reads, "If you aint dead, you win!"
